2.companyDescription: A Global powerhouse in leather, footwear, garments, PPE, safety gear, equestrian products, and premium accessories, MacBook Pro Landing  Limited stands at the forefront of craftsmanship and innovation. With 22+ state-of-the-art manufacturing units and a presence in 50+ countries, we combine traditional expertise with modern technology to deliver products that reflect quality, durability, and performance.
2.focusTitle: Special Focus: Safety Footwear – Innovation Meets Protection
2.focusDescription: At MacBook Pro Landing , safety footwear means confidence, comfort, and innovation. As a major supplier to global brands like Portwest, Uvex-Heckel, Feldtmann, Wurth, Stabilus, Coverguard, Itturi, and MTS, we produce footwear meeting EN ISO 20345, ASTM, and CSA standards.
2.focusAdditional: With 3 specialized factories producing 7,000 uppers and 6,000 pairs daily using 8 DESMA injection machines, we offer Rubber Vulcanized and Goodyear Welted shoes for industrial and military use. Backed by our LWG-certified tannery and SA 8000 & ISO 9001 certifications, we ensure ethical, sustainable, and globally compliant production.
bulletPoints: Ergonomic comfort with ankle support & cushioning
2.finalNote: Ideal for construction, mining, oil & gas, logistics, and manufacturing, our footwear combines protection, durability, and style. MacBook Pro Landing  – redefining safety footwear through innovation, quality, and sustainability.
2.footerCopyright: Copyright © 2025 MacBook Pro Landing  Group All Rights Reserved.
